data.description: Impeccably gorgeous 3-2.5-2 townhome in the perfect location just minutes from everything. This home is barely lived in & like-new. Shows like a model home! Open concept SMART home with natural lighting & durable wood-look tile for easy maintenance & glamorous appeal. Built-in, all electric kitchen with beautiful white shaker-style cabinetry, expansive island with seating, granite countertop, tile backsplash, walk-in & wrap-around pantry for plenty of storage. Relaxing, covered patio is the perfect place to enjoy a cup of coffee or a glass of wine. Convenient powder bath on first floor. All bedrooms are upstairs with laundry closet conveniently nearby. Spacious owner's suite featuring two walk-in closets, dual vanity sinks, linen closet & oversized shower. Secondary bedrooms complete with spacious walk-in closets. Bonus loft area on second floor perfect for reading nook, office or study space. Settle in @ this show-stopper just in time for the holidays! CAREFREE LIFESTYLE AT ITS BEST!
